 3, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2065657262128189856", "url": "https://x.com/TheWuhanClan/status/2065657262128189856", "text": "Iran isn’t going to accept Trump’s proposal to reopen the Strait of Hormuz &amp; give up its nukes because it would be admitting total defeat, accepting complete humiliation, giving up all leverage when their position is now stronger. They would rather die. #oott $es $spy $spx #iran", "time": "04:47", "author": "TheWuhanClan", "author_name": "Wuhan Fourth Turning Swan", "followers": 20042, "views": 444, "likes": 5, "replies": 3, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2065660448544788768", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2065660448544788768", "text": "The market seems to be discounting a return to the pre-war world\n\nBut it’s also discounting strong evidence for much higher long-term oil prices\n\nMarkets can live with uncertainty \n\nThey cannot function when government policy is to lie\n\n#OOTT #Oil #EnergyMarkets #WTI https://t.co/aJiRYdTFXn", "time": "05:00", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 6773, "likes": 64, "replies": 1, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 9, "labels": null}, {"id": "2065671295199482211", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2065671295199482211", "text": "Petrobras’ Chambriard Says Pemex CEO To Visit Brazil in June\n#oott https://t.co/yjh3mhadvw", "time": "05:43", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3181, "likes": 6, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2065705924052795500", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2065705924052795500", "text": "#Venezuela’s oil-linked debt with China could complicate its restructuring push #oott https://t.co/XBNb0igGMR", "time": "08:00", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3113, "likes": 7, "