or_name": "Sumit Ritolia", "followers": 402, "views": 4193, "likes": 37, "replies": 3, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 8, "labels": null}, {"id": "2065829972824965432", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2065829972824965432", "text": "U.S. now says a deal could be signed in \"days\" #OOTT", "time": "16:13", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "views": 2467, "likes": 8, "replies": 4, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2065831806973222962", "url": "https://x.com/Amalteya3000/status/2065831806973222962", "text": "I don’t understand why #Iran would sign a bad MOU now when it could wait until Sep when US #oil stocks will reach MOL (insted May) and it will get them upperhand.\nimo now is time for escalation, especially in SoH Southern Corridor\n#oott #wti", "time": "16:20", "author": "Amalteya3000", "author_name": "Amalteya", "followers": 773, "views": 6322, "likes": 35, "replies": 9, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2065867942277878025", "url": "https://x.com/Amalteya3000/status/2065867942277878025", "text": "The lowest level of #oil stocks in Cushing was 13 mb in 2004.\nNo one died.\nEnd of story.\n#oott #wti #eia", "time": "18:44", "author": "Amalteya3000", "author_name": "Amalteya", "followers": 773, "views": 17727, "likes": 71, "replies": 17, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2065876316981772504", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2065876316981772504", "text": "Ukrainian military hits Russia's oil infrastructure in Volgograd region, Kyiv says #oott https://t.co/OvGC9wYmYp", "time": "19:17", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 6363, "likes": 11, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2065876366722039864", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2065876366722039864", "text": "Poland to end capping fue